  "description" : "In the year 2025, huge beasts from beyond the galaxy attacked Earth. In the war that followed, humanity fought back with a giant robot named Yukio, piloted by Tetsuo Yabusame, As the massive alien swarm closed in on humanity`s homeworld, Tetsuo and the Earth Defense Force deployed for the final battle with the invading horde. They lost...\nSource: Viz",
